%term beta! srl ([x] %the (reduce (letb (bang M1) (M2 x)) _) red/beta!) ([x] [d] of/letb (Dof2 x d) (of/bang (%the (of _ T) (Dof1 x d)))) (linear/letb2 Dlin) (Dlin M1) %.
